        "mainpic": "bc6680d9-64ab-4986-b88d-ed3f18f91c8d",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Birch Landing 500 Maxham Rd Austell, GA 30168 Reach out via phone: show contact info Apartment Information: 2 Bedroom | 2.5 Bath Apartment Size: 1350 sq ft Monthly Price: $1479 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Lease Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Apartment Includes: ◾ Air Conditioning/Heating ◾ Balcony/Patio in Select Units ◾ Cable Ready ◾ Carpet ◾ Dining Room ◾ Extra Storage ◾ Garden Tub ◾ Handrails ◾ Hardwood Floors ◾ High Speed Internet Access ◾ Kitchen ◾ Office ◾ Range ◾ Refrigerator/Freezer ◾ Scenic View ◾ Trash Compactor ◾ Tub/Shower ◾ Vaulted Ceiling ◾ Walk-In Closets ◾ Washer/Dryer Hookup in Select Units Property Description: Whether you're preparing a meal in your beautiful gourmet kitchen, enjoying the fresh air out on your own private patio, or unwinding after a long day beside your cozy wood burning stone fireplace, you'll fall in love with where you live over and over again. With spacious, thoughtfully planned layouts and convenient extra features like full size washers and dryer connections, Garden Tubs, extra storage and an abundance of natural light, our apartments for rent in Austell, GA really do have it all. Come home to Birch Landing and discover what real living is all about. Property Amenities: ◾ BBQ/Picnic Area ◾ Business Center ◾ Clubhouse ◾ Conference Room ◾ Controlled Access Gate ◾ Indoor Pool & Jacuzzi ◾ Laundry Facilities ◾ Maintenance on site ◾ Online Services ◾ Parking ◾ Planned Social Activities ◾ Playground ◾ Preferred Employer Discounts Available ◾ Property Manager on Site ◾ Public Transportation ◾ Smoke Free ◾ Sparkling Outdoor Pool ◾ Storage Space ◾ Tennis Courts ◾ Townhomes Available Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/BirchLandingApartments/ Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=birch_landing&rp=qYZ1UT8Y6Yae&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=birch_landing&rp=qYZ1UT8Y6Yae&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=birch_landing&rp=qYZ1UT8Y6Yae&t=sch Reach out via phone: show contact info Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sun: 1:00 PM - 4:30 PM Pet Ownership Policy: We welcome 2 pets per apartment home. There is a maximum of 50lbs combined weight of 2 pets. There is a one-time pet fee of $325. Please call for complete pet policy information. $20 Pet Monthly Rent. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY A5EBCC31578F4B",
