        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome home to Birch Landing! Located at: 500 Maxham Rd Austell, GA 30168 Rental Information: # of Bedrooms: 1 # of Bathrooms: 1 Square Footage: 910 sq ft Monthly Price: $1090 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Call our office at show contact info Whether you're preparing a meal in your beautiful gourmet kitchen, enjoying the fresh air out on your own private patio, or unwinding after a long day beside your cozy wood burning stone fireplace, you'll fall in love with where you live over and over again. With spacious, thoughtfully planned layouts and convenient extra features like full size washers and dryer connections, Garden Tubs, extra storage and an abundance of natural light, our apartments for rent in Austell, GA really do have it all. Come home to Birch Landing and discover what real living is all about. Community Features: ◾ BBQ/Picnic Area ◾ Business Center ◾ Conference Room ◾ Courtesy Patrol ◾ High Speed Internet Available ◾ Indoor Pool & Jacuzzi ◾ Laundry Facilities ◾ Maintenance on site ◾ Online Services ◾ Parking ◾ Planned Social Activities ◾ Playground ◾ Property Manager on Site ◾ Recreational Areas ◾ Smoke Free ◾ Sparkling Outdoor Pool ◾ Storage Space ◾ Sunrooms ◾ Tennis Courts ◾ Townhomes Available Apartment Home Features: ◾ Air Conditioning/Heating ◾ Balcony/Patio in Select Units ◾ Carpet ◾ Dining Room ◾ Disposal ◾ Extra Storage ◾ Garden Tub ◾ Handrails ◾ Hardwood Floors ◾ High Speed Internet Access ◾ Kitchen ◾ Office ◾ Refrigerator/Freezer ◾ Scenic View ◾ Skylight ◾ Trash Compactor ◾ Tub/Shower ◾ Vaulted Ceiling ◾ Walk-In Closets ◾ Washer/Dryer Hookup in Select Units Office Hours: Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sun: 1:00 PM - 4:30 PM Call our office at show contact info Pet Policy: We welcome 2 pets per apartment home. There is a maximum of 50lbs combined weight of 2 pets. There is a one-time pet fee of $325. Please call for complete pet policy information. $20 Pet Monthly Rent. Leasing Options: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/BirchLandingApartments/ Website: www.lease-apts.com?n=birch_landing&rp=2yXj1qqCVQzv&t=wb Online Application: www.lease-apts.com?n=birch_landing&rp=2yXj1qqCVQzv&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.lease-apts.com?n=birch_landing&rp=2yXj1qqCVQzv&t=sch All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY 24BEDFD442184C",
