h owner and HOA approval ($350 non-refundable pet fee per approved pet). Credit, background, rental history, and income verification required. This move-in-ready townhome combines comfort, convenience, and an unbeatable Sandy Springs location. Schedule your private showing today! Property Type : Townhouse Pets : Cats, Small Dogs, Large Dogs Allowed Smoking : OUTSIDE_ONLY Lease Term : 2600.00 / Month 2600.00 Deposit Lease Length: Contact For Details Available: 09/01/2026 Occupancy Limit: 4 People Utilities Included : Sewage Water Garbage Recycling Appliances : Dishwasher Garbage Disposal Refrigerator Dryer Microwave Washer Freezer Range Oven Amenities : Cable Ready Fitness Center Swimming Pool Near Parks Secure Building Bicycle Parking Security Cameras Wired For Internet Balcony Or Deck Heating & Cooling : Forced Air Central Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6NjY4MjU3?property=1245429&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/6900-roswell-rd-sandy-springs-ga-unit-f4/cc66832c-de78-4321-abca-5e61277d3c41?source=craigslist",
