        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Polo Club Apartments Featured Floorplan: 2-bed / 2-bath / 1094 sq ft Monthly Price: $1154 *Optional and usage-based charges not included. Contact office to confirm pricing details and included fees. Deposit: $500 Call us for more information! show contact info Description: The living spaces at Polo Club Apartments are thoughtfully designed for comfort and convenience in mind, and are stylishly appointed with the kind of premium materials and finishes you won't find in any other rental apartments in Stone Mountain, GA. Urgent & Scroll-Stopping Now Leasing in Stone Mountain! Our 2BR / 2BA apartments won't last long! Move-in specials available for a limited time Schedule your visit today and secure your new home! #AffordableLiving #BudgetFriendlyHomes #NowLeasing #StoneMountainLiving #ApartmentDeals #MoveInSpecial #RentSmart #NewHomeVibes #AtlantaApartments Lease Terms: 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month Pet Policy: A maximum of 2 pets per unit shall be accepted. The pet fee is $350 Non-Refundable per pet. $30 monthly pet rent. A pet addendum must be completed, and pet fees must be paid prior to moving in. If there is more than one pet per unit, the combined weight of the 2 pets cannot exceed 50 lbs. For more information, please call our leasing office. Apartment Amenities: − Breakfast Bar − Cable Ready − Carpet − Dining Room − Dishwasher − Disposal − Extra Storage − Range − Tub/Shower − Vinyl Flooring − Air Conditioning and Gas Heating − Brushed Nickel Lighting Package − Cozy Fireplaces − Huge Floorplans up to 1300 sq. ft. − Newly Updated Apartments − Patio or Balcony − Roommate Floor Plans − Walk-In Closets − Washer & Dryer Connections Community Features: − Business Center − Clubhouse − Community Events − On Marta bus-line − Pet Care − Picnic Area − Playground − Tennis Court − Cardio & Fitness Center − Clothes Care Center − Electronic Rent Payment − Minutes to Stone Mountain park − On-Site Management − Package Receiving − Resort Style Swimming Pool − Shopping, Dining, and Entertainment Nearby Address: 100 Ashley Creek Cir Stone Mountain, GA 30083 Call us for more information! show contact info Mon - Fri: 8:30 AM - 5:30 PM Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM Sun: 1:00 PM - 5:00 PM Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/poloclubapartments Website: www.apts-rental.com?n=polo_club&rp=7wPCrXCRKFRY&t=wb Online Application: www.apts-rental.com?n=polo_club&rp=7wPCrXCRKFRY&t=ap Schedule a Tour: www.apts-rental.com?n=polo_club&rp=7wPCrXCRKFRY&t=sch Equal Housing Opportunity. All pricing, availability, fees, and terms are subject to change without notice. EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY D225BF0D9D4E426",
